<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="there-adv">there <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðeə(r)/    美 /ðer/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在那里；到那里；往那里：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We went on to Paris and stayed there eleven days.
我们接着去了巴黎，在那里待了11天。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-be">2.★ <strong>[与动词be连用表示存在]：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>there be:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was nothing I could do to make her happy, it seemed.
我似乎没有办法让她开心。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There are two reasons for choosing this park.
选择这个公园有两个理由。</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In some areas, there may be as much as 430 inches of rain annually.
一些地区的年降雨量可多达430英寸。</p><footer>2008 广东</footer></div>

<h4 id="3appear-live-remain-seemthere">3.<strong>[与appear, live, remain, seem等表示存在、状态等意义的词连用，there本身没有地点概念]：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At the underside of the ice shelf there lives a small fish.
在冰川底部生活着一种小鱼。</p><footer>2008 辽宁改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There remains a chance that Fred might still turn up alive.
弗雷德仍有可能活着回来。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[用以引起注意、加强语气等]：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Look, there come the rest of our guests!
看，我们其余的客人来了！</p><footer>2010 江苏</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There he comes now.
瞧，他来了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There goes the phone.
电话铃响了。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>在那一点上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There I disagree with you.
在那点上我不同意你的看法。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="over-there">over there</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在那里：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Who is the man standing over there?
站在那边的那个人是谁？</p></div>

<h3 id="be-always-there-for-sb">be (always) there (for sb)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[口语] 给予支持或援助：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father was always there for me with good advice.
我父亲总能给我好建议。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li><strong><em>_</em></strong>_ a certain doubt among the people as to the practical value of the project.  （2009 安徽）<br />
A.It has<br />
B.They have<br />
C.It remains<br />
D.There remains  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. D  </p></div>